title: Justin Timberlake Brings His Golden Good-Luck Charm to the Oscars - Wife Jessica Biel!
text:
Justin Timberlake and Jessica Biel at the 2017 Oscars Justin Timberlake Brings His Golden Good-Luck Charm to the Oscars — Wife Jessica Biel! February 26, 2017 Share This Link Copy What’s Your Reaction? Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 Justin Timberlake Brings His Golden Good-Luck Charm to the Oscars — Wife Jessica Biel! 
Justin Timberlake turned up to the Oscars looking like a million bucks on Sunday. The superstar is nominated for best original song for "Can't Stop the Feeling" from Trolls , and he brought along wife Jessica Biel . (He adorably referred to her golden dress as "perfection" on the red carpet.) Justin's on tap to perform the song, and as a quick reminder, this won't be his first time performing at the Academy Awards !
